Figs 42–43, 47
): Translucent throughout. Coecum of similar width to adjacent aedeagus, weakly bent. Aedeagus bent at posterior margin of coecum, and strongly bent before ventral extension over vesica, fairly straight in-between. Left flank of posterior ventral extension ("hood" over everted vesica) with a concave gouge and a convex posterior-lateral expansion (
Fig. 67
), right flank weakly convex (
Figs 62 & 67
), apex concave medially and convex on edges (
Fig. 62
